{"tid":1762284,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"由2019年6月12日起，熱血公民開始了對被捕者的法律支援服務","createTime":"2019-11-29T13:14:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-02T17:45:34.000Z","uid":73381,"like":11,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"3b720056c91a0f1f3adee954fd04fe64ec2efeea","tid":1762284,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T13:14:03.000Z","msg":"由2019年6月12日起，熱血公民開始了對被捕者的法律支援服務；<br />\n<br />\n在7月21日開始組織了安全車隊，在公共運輸服務斷絕下接送市民在衝突現場中平安回家；<br />\n<br />\n8月初開始對參與者提供事後創傷中醫或西醫免費治療，以及心理義診服務；<br />\n<br />\n11月協助拯救被圍困在香港中文大學及香港理工大學內的學生和參與者。"},{"pid":"75eb40017b3cb7e7e19d57109a58811d765930fd","tid":1762284,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T13:15:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0436c9e2e4d3d562e52d23ec32814b3266d67455","tid":1762284,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T13:18:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40588a9f86f519e4dcf964f755998b93102d7e6b","tid":1762284,"uid":77788,"like":4,"dislike":6,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T13:19:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4c9b9ae98b4d39e53b38c5f32d388090067873f1","tid":1762284,"uid":291065,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T13:20:18.000Z","msg":"善用起底功能"},{"pid":"62c21cad083a01e2540d57f6f7ea64c5af008bd3","tid":1762284,"uid":73381,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"40588a9f86f519e4dcf964f755998b93102d7e6b","tid":1762284,"uid":77788,"like":4,"dislike":6,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T13:19:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T13:20:52.000Z","msg":"幾時有叫人捐錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"789762bc88924ad5056280da164986310b3f340c","tid":17